// topics.rive

/**
 * All topics should include random to catch all triggers defined in the default topic (which is
 * hardcoded as the 'random' topic in Rivescript.
 */

// The campaign topic defines triggers to catch yes and no messages and call the confirmedCampaign
// and declinedCampaign macros respectively.
> topic campaign includes random

+ @yes [*]
- confirmedCampaign

+ (heck|hell|hells|hm|uh|why) @yes [*]
- confirmedCampaign

+ @no [*]
- declinedCampaign

< topic
